Text: About 9 years Ago. i had travel to Empat lawang regency for my college duty.
  I had stay in there about 22 days. even this village near from my home but they
  are really different from us. from language, Culture, Habit and view of live. and
  guess what I can passed this momment even I was so awkard and rigid for 1st time
  there.
